  • Package com.ibm.jaggr.core.impl.deps

    • Class com.ibm.jaggr.core.impl.deps.DepTree extends Object implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      -8494644438459736244L

      • Serialized Fields

        • depMap

          ConcurrentMap<K,V> depMap
          Map of directory names to DepTreeNode objects. Each DepTreeNode mirrors the associated file directory in terms of the directory structure and the javascript files contained therein. The file directories are orthogonal (i.e. non-overlapping). The DepTreeNode objects in this map can specify directory lists using module names with relative paths and do not contain any resolved dependency references to any other modules. They only contain the String array of dependency names for each javascript source file.

          This object gets serialized/de-serialized to/from the location specified by the basedir constructor argument.

        • rawConfig

          String rawConfig

        • stamp

          long stamp

        • cacheBust

          String cacheBust

        • fromCache

          boolean fromCache

      serialVersionUID:
      1202056345279875004L

      • Serialized Fields

        • booleanTerms

          Set<E> booleanTerms
          A Set of BooleanTerm objects. A BooleanTerm is a set of variable state objects that are logically and'ed together, while instances of this object are comprised of the set of BooleanTerms that are logically or-ed together.

          An empty set means that the expression evaluates to false.
          A null set means that the expression evaluates to true;

        • isSimplified

          boolean isSimplified
          True if the formula has been simplified.
